PrivyID akan memudahkan Anda dalam proses penandatanganan perjanjian/dokumen apapun yang nantinya perlu Anda setujui dengan Samir. Bersama dengan email ini, kami ingin menginformasikan bahwa saat ini kami belum dapat menerbitkan PrivyID Anda karena Dokumen Identitas diragukan keabsahannya. I recently encountered a troublesome situation with the PrivyID app. When my certificates expired, the app prompted me to submit my KTP and verify my email and phone number. However, the phone number verification process became a nightmare as the authentication code never showed up in my SMS. This happened across three different phone numbers, making it impossible for me to access crucial documents that required immediate attention. Frustrated, I had to resort to manual verification via the web chat bot they asked me to take a selfie with my KTP (which is super strange). While I'm glad the web chat bot responded quickly, the overall experience with the app's verification process has left me thoroughly disappointed. I can only give the app two stars for its unreliable verification process, hindering urgent tasks.
